    card for every 2 colors your Tamers have. Then, return 1 of their Digimon with
    1 or fewer digivolution cards to the hand.\n[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When
    your other Digimon are played or digivolve, if any of them have the [ADVENTURE]\_trait,
    1 of your Digimon gains \uFF1CAlliance\uFF1E for the turn. Then, 1 of your Digimon
    may attack."
